#. Description of the theme
#: style.css
msgid "An elegant, literary full-site-editing theme for writers, editors, and personal brands. Light Cormorant Garamond display headlines with italic accents, a calm Newsreader reading column, deep-teal and warm-ochre palette on a cream ground, numbered service cards, and gentle float accents that respect reduced-motion. Zero plugin dependencies, WCAG 2.2 AA accessible, Core Web Vitals optimised, self-hosted OFL fonts, RTL-ready via CSS logical properties."
msgstr ""

